uk.co.strangeskies.property

Interface Property<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the property.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LocaleManager, ObservableProperty<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IdentityExpression, IdentityProperty, LocaleManagerService, ObservablePropertyImpl

    public interface Property<T>
    This interface represents a gettable and settable property of a given type.
